### What is the minimum down payment for crane financing?

The minimum down payment typically starts at 10% of the equipment cost. However, the exact amount depends on factors such as your credit profile, business financials, and the type of crane you're financing. We can structure deals with higher down payments to reduce monthly obligations if that suits your cash flow better.

### Can I finance a used crane?

Yes, we offer financing for both new and used cranes. The age and condition of the equipment will affect the financing terms, including interest rate and loan tenure. Used cranes can provide excellent value, and our team can help you assess whether a used crane is a good investment for your business.

